snippet.textDisplay:
I got introduced to coke studio by the song 'Allahu Akbar' and needless to say was mesmerized by it, the tune stayed in my heart.It had a great impact on me that immediately I checked out most of the songs.I was just spellbound.Magical songs with such lyrics that will make anyone's heart melt.It's pure bliss on earth.All of the coke studio songs are on my phone's playlist and on YouTube favourites for lifetime.Sometimes I listen the gems in a loop on and on.We are brothers and we should definitely appreciate our good things.The dedication,effort, passion you guys make behind these needs to be praised.For the first time made this long comment on any video.
Ultra talented singers, magical songs filled with emotions and Momina, you are my crush now,!
Love from India,keep spreading love.💗
